8
00:00:16,000 --> 00:00:20,711
We traveled between universes. Isn't that a fantasy at all?

9
00:00:20,711 --> 00:00:22,430
Congratulations!

10
00:00:22,430 --> 00:00:23,808
Okay.

11
00:00:23,808 --> 00:00:25,408
Bye.

12
00:00:31,040 --> 00:00:33,820
Som and Prae called.

13
00:00:33,820 --> 00:00:37,420
