20
00:00:57,080 --> 00:00:59,532
I don't want to kick you at all.

21
00:01:01,120 --> 00:01:05,300
What should we do now?

22
00:01:05,300 --> 00:01:08,540
Does it mean the matching system isn't reliable?

23
00:01:08,540 --> 00:01:10,040
Calm down.

24
00:01:10,040 --> 00:01:14,220
The matching system was only built to help us find probability.

25
00:01:14,220 --> 00:01:16,242
