29
00:01:28,560 --> 00:01:30,000
Yes.

30
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:35,224
The best advice I have for you right now is...

31
00:01:35,224 --> 00:01:38,020
follow your heart.

32
00:01:53,520 --> 00:01:57,763
