33
00:01:57,763 --> 00:01:59,660
Why?

34
00:01:59,660 --> 00:02:00,940
Think about it.

35
00:02:00,940 --> 00:02:04,280
It's extremely difficult to match someone.

36
00:02:04,280 --> 00:02:06,720
And we don't know if that's the right one until we dream.

37
00:02:06,720 --> 00:02:08,593
So many conditions that I'm discouraged.

38
00:02:08,593 --> 00:02:10,510
