139
00:09:54,673 --> 00:09:57,890
It's for the best if you come.

140
00:09:57,890 --> 00:10:00,463
- What?
- Come on.

141
00:10:01,920 --> 00:10:03,530
Quickly.

142
00:10:03,530 --> 00:10:04,800
The bread.

143
00:10:04,800 --> 00:10:07,146
Leave it. Let's go.

144
00:10:09,640 --> 00:10:12,280
We have two opinions here.

145
00:10:12,280 --> 00:10:14,650
Tun and I think we should have a happy ending.

146
00:10:14,650 --> 00:10:18,130
