176
00:11:27,120 --> 00:11:30,330
Then you collect files from us and put together a presentation.

177
00:11:31,560 --> 00:11:32,720
But I'm not...

178
00:11:32,720 --> 00:11:35,020
You're not what?

179
00:11:35,020 --> 00:11:37,010
He's not feeling well.

180
00:11:37,010 --> 00:11:39,010
Right, Tun?

181
00:11:39,920 --> 00:11:41,820
Yes.

182
00:11:44,880 --> 00:11:47,764
I'm having the flu.

183
00:11:49,340 --> 00:11:51,370
He's burning up.

184
00:11:51,370 --> 00:11:54,790
Tun, you're a workaholic.

185
00:11:54,790 --> 00:11:57,040
