186
00:11:57,040 --> 00:11:59,600
But we were still working like it was nothing.

187
00:11:59,600 --> 00:12:01,500
You're right.

188
00:12:02,240 --> 00:12:04,520
Fine. I'll do it.

189
00:12:04,520 --> 00:12:05,560
See?

190
00:12:05,560 --> 00:12:09,180
I knew someone like you would never ditch work.

191
00:12:09,180 --> 00:12:10,780
Right?

192
00:12:13,997 --> 00:12:16,060
