198
00:12:25,627 --> 00:12:28,000
A short sentence that makes movies more appealing.

199
00:12:28,000 --> 00:12:33,348
I can't even rhyme words in poems, let alone the tagline.

200
00:12:33,348 --> 00:12:35,667
Can you even handle this?

201
00:12:35,667 --> 00:12:37,056
Let me help.

202
00:12:37,056 --> 00:12:40,843
I can. I will come up with something eventually.

203
00:12:42,960 --> 00:12:45,580
