205
00:12:47,660 --> 00:12:50,120
Am I a joke to you, Tess?

206
00:12:50,120 --> 00:12:52,428
No, Dad.

207
00:12:53,900 --> 00:12:55,240
Has he picked up yet?

208
00:12:55,240 --> 00:12:56,479
No.

209
00:12:56,479 --> 00:12:59,411
