221
00:13:42,570 --> 00:13:45,316
You came for me, darling?

222
00:13:48,677 --> 00:13:51,120
I'm sorry. My friend is drunk.

223
00:13:51,120 --> 00:13:53,184
May you excuse me?

224
00:13:57,770 --> 00:13:59,970
Tun.

225
00:13:59,970 --> 00:14:01,630
