226
00:14:01,630 --> 00:14:03,500
Not trying to be.

227
00:14:03,500 --> 00:14:06,940
Pull yourself together.

228
00:14:06,940 --> 00:14:08,480
Tess,

229
00:14:08,480 --> 00:14:10,610
