231
00:14:12,750 --> 00:14:14,350
Shit.

232
00:14:15,980 --> 00:14:17,880
What should we do?

233
00:14:19,610 --> 00:14:22,090
What the hell are you doing, Tun?

234
00:14:22,090 --> 00:14:25,140
We've worked so hard.

235
00:14:25,140 --> 00:14:27,720
