236
00:14:28,750 --> 00:14:32,279
Hey, I didn't mean to.

237
00:14:34,750 --> 00:14:39,632
Who would know this guy is such a lightweight?

238
00:14:42,670 --> 00:14:44,303
What the heck are you talking about?

239
00:14:44,303 --> 00:14:46,860
Never mind.

240
00:14:46,860 --> 00:14:48,687
Hey, guys.

241
00:14:48,687 --> 00:14:50,640
Look on the bright side.

242
00:14:50,640 --> 00:14:54,583
