243
00:14:55,610 --> 00:15:00,310
And... Tess will talk to his dad for us.

244
00:15:01,950 --> 00:15:04,720
Where is your work file?

245
00:15:04,720 --> 00:15:06,520
Work file?

246
00:15:07,630 --> 00:15:10,520
Ah! In my thumb drive.

247
00:15:10,520 --> 00:15:13,064
I have it with me. Let me find it.

248
00:15:35,380 --> 00:15:37,080
