249
00:15:39,360 --> 00:15:43,150
Tun, I have a serious question.

250
00:15:43,150 --> 00:15:45,610
The promise we made,

251
00:15:45,610 --> 00:15:47,310
did you forget all about it?

252
00:15:47,310 --> 00:15:49,480
Huh?

253
00:15:49,480 --> 00:15:51,780
